
'''''Behind the scenes''''' is a [[popularity|popular]] term that refers to  the actual workings of an endeavor, as opposed to what is normally perceived in the [[public view]]. Literally, it means the backstage perspective in a [[theatre|theatrical]] production, where the entire machinery of the staged event is revealed. In wider usage, it at times implies [[secret]] practices and [[hidden agenda]]s, although it often simply refers to a detailed [[insider]]'s view of how things work.

